2.0.0
-----

Meson build system

No external dependency

Static library support for MCU targets

Modularization of the source code, which now only contains:
  - libfusionsound core library
  - a generic sound driver for supported operating systems (only Linux for now)
    (on Linux OS, legacy OSS or modern ALSA sound driver)
  - the WAVE music provider

Separate packages for:
  - additional sound drivers
  - additional music providers
